commits.author: khanmjk
commits.message: Add comprehensive unit tests for various services - Implement tests for AboutService, including summary extraction and YouTube API mapping. - Add tests for AIService, focusing on formatting AI stats and validating systems. - Create tests for CapacityService, covering leave calculations and capacity adjustments. - Introduce tests for D3Service, ensuring availability checks and instance exposure. - Develop tests for FeedbackService, validating submission and context inclusion. - Implement tests for ForecastService, simulating team sizes and hiring rates. - Add tests for FrappeGanttService, checking library availability and instance creation. - Create tests for GanttService, normalizing IDs and computing estimates. - Introduce tests for GoalService, adding and updating goals with linked initiatives. - Implement tests for InitiativeService, ensuring addition, updates, and planning year validation. - Add tests for MarkdownService, checking rendering with and without the library. - Create tests for MermaidService, building theme configs and appending SVGs. - Introduce tests for OrgService, managing engineers and teams. - Implement tests for PlanningService, calculating team load summaries and planning data. - Add tests for RoadmapService, deriving quarters and date boundaries. - Create tests for SettingsService, ensuring defaults and preference storage. - Implement tests for SystemService, managing system initialization and activation. - Add tests for ThemeService, generating random themes and returning theme lists. - Create tests for VisualizationService, building dependency graphs and preparing tables. - Implement tests for WorkPackageService, ensuring work package creation and date recalculations. - Add tests for AppState, managing nested state and subscriber notifications. - Create tests for styleVars utility, setting CSS custom properties on elements. - Configure Vitest for testing environment setup.

Add comprehensive unit tests for various services - Implement tests for AboutService, including summary extraction and YouTube API mapping. - Add tests for AIService, focusing on formatting AI stats and validating systems. - Create tests for CapacityService, covering leave calculations and capacity adjustments. - Introduce tests for D3Service, ensuring availability checks and instance exposure. - Develop tests for FeedbackService, validating submission and context inclusion. - Implement tests for ForecastService, simulating team sizes and hiring rates. - Add tests for FrappeGanttService, checking library availability and instance creation. - Create tests for GanttService, normalizing IDs and computing estimates. - Introduce tests for GoalService, adding and updating goals with linked initiatives. - Implement tests for InitiativeService, ensuring addition, updates, and planning year validation. - Add tests for MarkdownService, checking rendering with and without the library. - Create tests for MermaidService, building theme configs and appending SVGs. - Introduce tests for OrgService, managing engineers and teams. - Implement tests for PlanningService, calculating team load summaries and planning data. - Add tests for RoadmapService, deriving quarters and date boundaries. - Create tests for SettingsService, ensuring defaults and preference storage. - Implement tests for SystemService, managing system initialization and activation. - Add tests for ThemeService, generating random themes and returning theme lists. - Create tests for VisualizationService, building dependency graphs and preparing tables. - Implement tests for WorkPackageService, ensuring work package creation and date recalculations. - Add tests for AppState, managing nested state and subscriber notifications. - Create tests for styleVars utility, setting CSS custom properties on elements. - Configure Vitest for testing environment setup.

architecturePhases.title: Genesis
architecturePhases.subtitle: The First Lines of Code
architecturePhases.description: It started with a single commit. A README and an index.html - the digital equivalent of breaking ground on a new building.

architecturePhases.title: The Planning Era
architecturePhases.subtitle: From Chaos to Structure
architecturePhases.description: Annual planning features begin to emerge. The codebase starts to find its purpose.

architecturePhases.title: Monolith Busting
architecturePhases.subtitle: Breaking the Big File
architecturePhases.description: The massive index.html is finally broken apart into separate modules, marking a major refactor point.

architecturePhases.title: The Component Revolution
architecturePhases.subtitle: Modular Thinking Takes Hold
architecturePhases.description: The js/components directory is born. Views are encapsulated, reusable, testable.

architecturePhases.title: AI Awakens
architecturePhases.subtitle: Intelligence Enters the Codebase
architecturePhases.description: AI features emerge - context-aware chat, smart suggestions, automated workflows.

architecturePhases.title: Workspace Layout
architecturePhases.subtitle: The Sidebar Era
architecturePhases.description: Navigation moves to a persistent sidebar. The concept of a 'Workspace' with swappable views is introduced.

architecturePhases.title: UI Theme Styling
architecturePhases.subtitle: Dark Mode & Theming
architecturePhases.description: Introduction of semantic CSS variables and comprehensive dark mode support.

architecturePhases.title: Agent Contracts
architecturePhases.subtitle: Rules for Robots
architecturePhases.description: Formal contracts (docs/*.md) are established to guide AI agents in maintaining code quality and consistency.

architecturePhases.title: Service Layer Architecture
architecturePhases.subtitle: Separation of Concerns
architecturePhases.description: The codebase had grown wild. Views were talking to each other, business logic was scattered. It was time for the Service Revolution.

architecturePhases.title: Tech Debt Paydown
architecturePhases.subtitle: Focus on Compliance
architecturePhases.description: A dedicated phase for cleaning up technical debt, improving compliance, and standardizing patterns.

architecturePhases.title: Code Quality Gates
architecturePhases.subtitle: Automated Standards
architecturePhases.description: Linting (ESLint) and Testing (Vitest) configurations are added, enforcing strict quality gates for all changes.

architecturePhases.title: Modern Era
architecturePhases.subtitle: Testing and CI/CD Maturity
architecturePhases.description: Unit tests arrive. Linting enforced. The codebase becomes a professional-grade project.
